---
title: Smokey Bacon & Mushroom Stroganoff with Garlic Rice & Parsley
description: Usually a stroganoff is a meat-heavy meal, but this one proves you can have all that heartiness in a veggie-fueled dish. Mushrooms take centre stage here, cooked in a creamy, smokey sauce and served tumbling over fragrant garlic rice and added bacon. We can’t wait for this one.
